   :feedback_c: Of course.  Write code little-by-little to gain confidence
   :answer_d: Watch unrelated videos while you program to stay loose
   :feedback_d: Distractions are probably not helpful
   :answer_e: Understand what you are trying to accomplish
   :feedback_e: Yes.  You must understand what you want to do
